  "title": "Social Worker @ Hougang Sheng Hong Family Service Centre",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibility Areas</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide casework management to clients with varying needs, risk and safety concerns.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with internal and external stakeholders to achieve case plan outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Participate/ implement group work to target client groups or other stakeholders/ agencies.</li>\n  <li>Participate in community development initiatives and provide recommendations for consideration.</li>\n  <li>Perform other duties as assigned by the Assistant Director &amp; Head of FSC/Director/Management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Required qualifications and experience</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree, Graduate Diploma or Master in Social Work / Degree or Master in Counselling.</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply. Experience working with individuals/ families is an added advantage.</li>\n  <li>Good report writing skill.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Good organisational skill.</li>\n</ul>",
